Package gov.ca.water.calgui.batch

DWR-supplied helper classes for running CalLite in parallel (multiple threads) or on a single thread

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RunScenarios
    This class will run the multiple batch files created when running on multiple threads.
    Singleton
    This class is used to run a single study of the wrimsv2 class.
